Hazrat shaikh masood kirmani masjid ka naam hazrat shaikh masood kirmani sarkar ke naam par rakha  gaya hai jo aaj se 400 saal qabal afganistaan se yaha ambajogai me tashreef laye the.

Hazrat's aim was to give the invitation to Islam to the people and in this simple way he laid the foundation of the mosque in the form of Mominabad and invited the people to Islam.
The name of Hazrat Shaikh Masood Kirmani Sarkar comes from the oldest elder in the world of Mominabad.
Mashallah
